data.description: NO HOA Everyone! Freedom and Convenience in one place.  Location Location Location Maitland/Altamonte Springs. NEW ROOF. Seminole County Schools!  This Single Family Home features 4 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, Split Floor Plan, Living room, Dining room and Dinette/Breakfast Room. Ample foyer with a Coat Closet. The layout allows access to the kitchen from both sides of the house. Full Air Conditioned Game room in laminate floors makes an incredible entertainment area for your family. Laminate and tile floors in the common areas. Oversized Beach Shutter Windows allow lots of natural light in the home. A gorgeous French Door gives you access to the POOL area, oversized yard, fully fenced around, pool deck and a shed for storage. Long driveway. Electrical Panel was replaced in 2019. 2 Miles away from the Altamonte Springs Mall, Starbucks, Cranes Roost, and restaurants. 30 Mis from Walt Disney World, 25 mins from Universal Studios, 30 mins away from SeaWorld. Call and Schedule your private showing today!
